data.description: This is the one! Beautiful 5+ acre setting surrounds this lovely ranch, over a full finished basement. 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, 1/2 bath on main. Cathedral ceilings, and stone fireplace in great room. Primary bedroom has huge walk-in closet, with laundry, and washer and dryer included. Basement is its own full home, complete with 2 large bedrooms, office, full kitchen with island, full bath, and 1/2 bath, separate entry, and living room. Could be in-law suite, or rental income? Back yard has a LARGE deck, to watch the deer in the woods! Exterior has just been fully painted. New this past summer is an above ground pool, with sitting deck. 2 story barn for chickens, livestock, storage, or kids' playhouse.
